39
00:01:48,110 --> 00:01:49,340
Excuse me?

40
00:01:49,350 --> 00:01:50,240
My daughter in law.

41
00:01:50,910 --> 00:01:53,670
You must really love your daughter in law.

42
00:01:53,670 --> 00:01:55,540
She's going to be a writer.

43
00:01:55,550 --> 00:01:58,690
