77
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:06,790
Me too.

78
00:05:08,070 --> 00:05:09,790
I thought that, too.

79
00:05:11,300 --> 00:05:12,730
Really?

80
00:05:16,050 --> 00:05:17,900
You're the best.

81
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:32,140
Hobak.

82
00:05:32,150 --> 00:05:34,040
