84
00:05:36,050 --> 00:05:37,290
No...

85
00:05:37,300 --> 00:05:39,660
You don't look so well.

86
00:05:39,670 --> 00:05:41,770
Are you coming down with something?

87
00:05:42,650 --> 00:05:44,270
I think I'm just tired.

88
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:47,400
Uncle, what's up?

89
00:05:47,410 --> 00:05:49,440
